version_description: Includes both Chords and tabs. Only tabs where it's needed. Both guitars included.
The original has a lot of synths and different guitar parts, this is a version for someone who wants to play the song on one guitar.
The chords of Shopping For Blood, nothing special.
The Chords of Swallow Smile, important: Not standard Tuning.
This tab has the chords in addition to the tab without any clutter or transposition. and additionally it is much more neat and clear than the other versions
